foundry-welcome (1.0.2) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Add src/qml/pages/qmldir so Qt6 can resolve CommunityPage, IntroPage,
    and ToolsPage from the "import ./pages" directory import in main.qml.
    Without qmldir, Qt6 refuses to import a subdirectory and the app crashes
    on startup with "CommunityPage is not a type".

 -- Will Norris <wbnorris@gmail.com>  Sun, 25 May 2026 00:00:00 +0700

foundry-welcome (1.0.1) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Add build.sh so package builds via dpkg-buildpackage on the target Ubuntu
    release, ensuring dpkg-shlibdeps captures Qt 6.9.2 sonames (not 6.10.2).

 -- Will Norris <wbnorris@gmail.com>  Sun, 25 May 2026 00:00:00 +0700

foundry-welcome (1.0.0) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Initial release. QML/Kirigami welcome screen for Foundry Linux:
    intro page, tools summary, and community links. Show-once sentinel at
    ~/.config/foundry-welcome-shown; XDG autostart via /etc/xdg/autostart.

